docs.abstract: For decades, Gavin de Becker has counseled governments, celebrities and countless readers on how to ward off threats and stay safe in a scary world.

docs.abstract: The president wants the Fed to cut rates and stimulate the economy. But the Fed appears poised to continue its patient stance at its meeting that ends Wednesday.
